  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Spinal Cord Injury (paraplegia or quadriplegia)

          -  Vitamin D deficiency

          -  Absolute deficient Vitamin D [25(OH)D] &lt; 16 ng/ml

          -  Relative deficient Vitamin D [25(OH)D] &lt;30ng/ml - participation in the FES/SRT study
             at Kessler Institute for Rehabilitation

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  History of kidney stones

          -  History of bone disorders

          -  Currently pregnant
      </textblock>
